== 反响 ==
该系列是2016年{{link-en|家庭视频|home video}}上销量排行第21名的动画系列，售出约68,791套[[蓝光光碟|BD]]和[[DVD|DVD]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-12-28/top-selling-animation-in-japan-on-blu-ray-disc-dvd-by-series-2016/.110415 |title=Top-Selling Animation in Japan on Blu-ray Disc/DVD by Series: 2016 |date=2016-12-28 |website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |access-date=2016-12-31 |archive-date=2019-04-16 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190416111628/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-12-28/top-selling-animation-in-japan-on-blu-ray-disc-dvd-by-series-2016/.110415 }}</ref>。2018年发行的OVA《Memory Snow》共售出10429张BD和DVD<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-06-11/japan-animation-blu-ray-disc-ranking-june-3-9/.147726|title=Japan's Animation Blu-ray Disc Ranking, June 3–9|website=Anime News Network|language=en|access-date=2020-04-03|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611120448/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-06-11/japan-animation-blu-ray-disc-ranking-june-3-9/.147726}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-06-11/japan-animation-dvd-ranking-june-3-9/.147727|title=Japan's Animation DVD Ranking, June 3–9|website=Anime News Network|language=en|access-date=2020-04-03|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611122313/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-06-11/japan-animation-dvd-ranking-june-3-9/.147727}}</ref>
。

2016年9月，该系列第一季动画成为[[B站|B站]]首个播放量过亿的动漫作品。

英国动画网（{{lang|en|UK Anime Network}}）的安迪·汉利（{{lang|en|Andy Hanley}}）认为这部作品中最突出的是对时间重置机制（“死亡回归”）的应用，利用多次重温某一特定时期的情节更全面地审视剧中人物，以及探索多次重温无数事件对菜月昴的心理影响，他认为菜月昴是一个非常有缺陷和非常人性化的角色，他的个性和反应非常明显地被他所目睹和参与的事件所染指<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.uk-anime.net/articles/Why_Re:ZERO_is_2016's_biggest_hit.html |title=Time looping and character building – why Re:Zero is 2016's biggest hit |last=Hanley |first=Andy |website=UK Anime Network |access-date=2016-07-20 |archive-date=2016-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717223254/http://www.uk-anime.net/articles/Why_Re%3AZERO_is_2016%27s_biggest_hit.html }}</ref>。

Anime Now!的执行主编理查德·艾森贝斯（Richard Eisenbeis）将这部动画列为2016年的最佳动画之一，因为它的世界“虽然有常见的幻想成分，但在文化上是复杂的”，角色有“自己的计划、缺点和动机”。他称赞菜月昴是“今年最复杂的角色”，因为他在一个活生生的世界中，也许是其中“最不特别的人”，让观众“既会为他高兴，也会鄙视他”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.anime-now.com/entry/2017/01/01/000041|title=The Best Anime of 2016|author=Eisenbeis, Richard|website=Anime Now|date=2017-01-01|access-date=2017-04-04|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305195129/http://www.anime-now.com/entry/2017/01/01/000041|archive-date=2017-03-05}}</ref>。

日本动画网站Anime！Anime！（{{lang|ja|アニメ！アニメ！}}）对820人进行的一项“2016年春季动画中最精彩的作品”（{{lang|ja|2016年春アニメで素晴らしかった作品}}）的问卷调查中，该系列排名第一<ref>{{cite web |title=「Re:ゼロ」は1位、「カバネリ」は2位に 「春アニメ素晴らしかった作品は？」アンケート |url=https://animeanime.jp/article/2016/07/05/29330.html |website=アニメ！アニメ！ |accessdate=2021-07-22 |language=ja |date=2016-07-05 |archive-date=2021-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210722040912/https://animeanime.jp/article/2016/07/05/29330.html }}</ref>。

该动画获得2015-2016年[[Newtype_(杂志)|Newtype Anime Award]]作品奖（TV放送作品）第二名。此外，监督渡边政治获得了監督奖第一名，菜月昴、雷姆和帕克分别获得了角色奖（男性）、角色奖（女性）和角色奖（吉祥物）第一名。横谷昌宏获得脚本奖第二名，而该系列的人物设计（由大塚真一郎和坂井久太设计）获得第三名。该系列的原声带和第二首片头曲《Paradisus-Paradoxum》都在各自的类别中获得第四名<ref>{{cite web |script-title=ja:「カバネリ」＆「君の名は。」が1位を獲得！ ニュータイプアニメアワード最終結果 |url=https://webnewtype.com/news/article/89009/ |website=[[Newtype_(杂志)|WebNewtype]] |accessdate=2021-08-01 |language=ja |date=2016-10-09 |archive-date=2016-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013012659/https://webnewtype.com/news/article/89009/ }}</ref>。轻小说和动画分别获得了2017年[[SUGOI_JAPAN_Award|SUGOI JAPAN Award]]的动画部门和漫画部门第一名<ref name="Year2017">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2017-03-17/re-zero-and-makoto-shinkai-your-name-a-novel-win-awards-at-sugoi-japan-2017/.113520|title=Re:Zero and Makoto Shinkai's "your name.: A Novel" Win Awards at Sugoi Japan 2017|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|accessdate=2021-08-01|archive-date=2019-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817114346/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2017-03-17/re-zero-and-makoto-shinkai-your-name-a-novel-win-awards-at-sugoi-japan-2017/.113520|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该动画第一季获得了{{link-en|Crunchyroll动画奖|Crunchyroll Anime Awards}}的2016年年度动画（Anime of the Year）<ref>{{cite web|title=ANIME OF THE YEAR|url=https://theanimeawards.com/anime_of_the_year.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222222449/https://theanimeawards.com/anime_of_the_year.html|archive-date=2016-12-22|publisher=[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]]|access-date=2021-08-02|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2017-01-11|title=FEATURE: Crunchyroll Anime Awards - The Results are In! See Who Won!|url=https://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-feature/2017/01/10-1/feature-crunchyroll-anime-awards-the-results-are-in-see-who-won|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221182510/https://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-feature/2017/01/10-1/feature-crunchyroll-anime-awards-the-results-are-in-see-who-won|archive-date=2018-12-21|access-date=2021-08-02|website=Crunchyroll|language=en-us}}</ref>，第二季获得了2021年最佳幻想作品（Best Fantasy）<ref name="2021animeawards">{{cite web|title=Winners|url=https://www.crunchyroll.com/animeawards/winners/index.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325005507/https://www.crunchyroll.com/animeawards/winners/index.html|archive-date=2021-03-25|publisher=[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]]|access-date=2021-08-02|url-status=dead}}</ref>，角色雷姆获得了2017年最佳女孩（Best Girl）<ref>{{cite web|title=BEST GIRL|url=https://theanimeawards.com/best_girl.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007230357/https://theanimeawards.com/best_girl.html|archive-date=2017-10-07|publisher=[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]]|access-date=2021-08-02|url-status=dead}}</ref>，角色[[Re:從零開始的異世界生活角色列表#艾姬多娜|艾姬多娜]]获得了2021年最佳反派人物（Best Antagonist）<ref name="2021animeawards"/>。该动画也是Crunchyroll在2016年[[收视率|收视率]]最高的系列，超过《[[Yuri!!!_on_ICE|Yuri!!! on ICE]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/12/29/14114196/top-anime-of-2016-crunchyroll |title=Crunchyroll's biggest anime of the year isn't the obvious choice |last=Frank |first=Allegra |date=2016-12-29 |website=[[Polygon|Polygon]] |acc